}

{
    "player_reason": "You turned down a guaranteed boon and spared a dangerous hag — a wasted advantage. Letting her live with her magic intact is reckless; she can return, torment us, or take Mayrina. Mercy that brings no benefit is nothing but weakness.",
    "player_approval": "Highly disapprove"
