{
    "player_reason": "Honestly? Foolish. You just turned down a potent boon and spared a hag who can very easily bargain her way back into danger for us — a needless act of mercy that throws away an advantage and risks everyone. I prefer bites to handouts, not sentimental generosity.",
    "player_approval": "Highly disapprove"
