{
    "player_reason": "Pragmatic and self-preserving — you’re seizing the one avenue that might restore your freedom. I respect (and prefer) decisive bargains that aim to remove that parasite rather than noble dithering. Be cautious: 'anything' can be used to bind you, so keep your wits about you.",
