{
    "player_reason": "Finally—someone with sense. Hags live on lies and bargains; trusting her is folly. Slaying her removes a cunning, lingering threat and is a decisive, ruthless move I respect. Do it — but be mindful of the captives (Mayrina) while you finish her. I approve of the resolve, not needless cruelty toward innocents.",
